            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>ucius</ex></expan> Folcinius <expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>uci</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilius</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>aius</ex></expan> Fabius <supplied reason="lost"><gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilius</ex></expan></supplied> duomvirum <note>sic</note> pavi<supplied reason="lost">m</supplied>en<supplied reason="lost">tum faci</supplied>un<supplied reason="lost">d</supplied>um <expan><abbr>dederun</abbr><ex>t</ex></expan> eis<supplied reason="lost">demque probaverunt</supplied>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Die Inschrift besteht bis [faci]um aus weißen Mosaiksteinen, danach aus schwarzen; sie gehört zum republikanischen Tempel. (B): Calabi-Limentani, AE 1978, Frova, AE 1984: Folconi[u]s; pav[im]en[tum.</p>
            </div>
